    <p>
      All products sold on fab4kids are digital downloads (PDF and Word documents).
      Under the Consumer Contracts Regulations 2013, you have the right to cancel a
      digital purchase within 14 days, <strong>unless you have already downloaded
      the content</strong>. By clicking &ldquo;Checkout&rdquo; and proceeding to payment,
      you acknowledge that digital delivery will begin immediately upon payment and
      that you waive your right to cancel once a download link has been provided.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have not downloaded your file and wish to cancel within 14 days of
